{"tid":1502302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再嘈 聽日究竟葵芳定機場？？？？","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T18:42:12.000Z","uid":266736,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"30c1378848f05795724d4fb4875f2f1be01d7c39","tid":1502302,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日荃葵友一定要留低！<br />\n其他區想入機場嘅就自己入機場！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n18區除咗荃葵青區 無曬人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他區要入機場嘅都夠做啦<br />\n荃葵行完嘅人要入機場自然會入<br />\n咁想入機場咪自己入囉<br />\n叫人唔好去荃葵係咩居心呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">送頭？？</span><br />\n依家18區街坊行出街食個飯都有事啦<br />\n送乜頭呀<br />\n安全嘅野大家自己衡量<br />\n唔好叫人唔好入荃葵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n要揸春袋？？</span><br />\n春袋自己識飛？聽日會唔見撚咗？<br />\n日日揸都得啦 有分時候嘅咩？<br />\n但聽日荃青遊行就得一次<br />\n係咪咁都要spin呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講曬 送唔送頭 自己衡量<br />\n到時行完要點 交俾現場決定啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">荃葵青好慘<br />\n荃灣手足被人斬無人理<br />\n葵芳地鐘tg放題無人理<br />\n青衣次次有咩活動都好似孤島咁(知係地勢問題，但都係姐）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日荃葵友一定要留低！<br />\n其他區想入機場嘅就自己入機場！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8195ec265cadf30dadca6af730d5cbf2677aec07","tid":1502302,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68f2e78d44f37a2159185403e9e16af5345defb0","tid":1502302,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0a8e2a7b6522e642ead6938e